1. Test with a valid file path as a command-line argument.
2. Test with an invalid file path as a command-line argument.
3. Test with an empty file.
4. Test with a file containing only comments.
5. Test with a file containing only whitespace.
6. Test with a file containing valid Monty bytecode commands.
7. Test with a file containing invalid Monty bytecode commands.
8. Test with a file containing a mix of valid and invalid Monty bytecode commands.
9. Test with a file containing a single valid Monty bytecode command.
10. Test with a file containing multiple valid Monty bytecode commands.